This Project is for Spring Core Dependency Injection


A)Maven

1)spring-context springframework dependency.

B)Dependency Injection

a)Application Context
1)Application context - XML Based Config.
2)Application context - getBean which you made to make object and inject it into reference.

b)XML Based Configuration
1)XML File - Define a Bean in this XML File.

c)Annotation Based Configuration

1)XML File - Define a ComponentScan in this XML File.
2)Model Class - @Component
3)Make Object and Inject in reference - @Autowired

d)Configuration using Class

1)@Configuration to define the Class.
2)@Bean() to define beans inside Class.